A set of sripts and some presentation material to introduce git

ALPHA QUALITY!

Alec Clews <alecclews@gmail.com>

GitHub repo at http://github.com/alecthegeek/demoGit.git

The scripts in thi repo are meant to demostrate certain aspectcs of using Git

They depenin on Git, gitk and bash


1) demoGitBranchMerge

Creates a repo
Creates 2 text files + .gitignore
Add and commits
Tag
Updates text files
Add and commit
Checkout tag
Create branch1
Updates text files
Add and commit
Updates text files
Add and commit
Checkout master
Updates text files
Add and commit
Perform merge  NB Conflicts
Resolve
Add and commit


2) demoGitRebase

Creates a repo
Creates 2 text files + .gitignore
Add and commits
Tag
Updates text files
Add and commit
Checkout tag
Create branch1
Updates text files
Add and commit
Updates text files
Add and commit
Checkout master
Updates text files
Add and commit
Perform rebase (no conflicts)

